p2p.title: Ukushintshanisana Kwabantu Ngabanye
p2p.description: Zibandakanye ekuhwebeni okuvikelekile kwe-cryptocurrency kwabantu ngabantu ngokuvikelwa kwe-escrow, izindlela zokukhokha eziguquguqukayo, namanani ancintisanayo.

portfolio.title: I-Portfolio
portfolio.description: Iqoqo eliphelele lokulawula i-portfolio lokulandelela izimpahla, ukuhlaziya ukusebenza, nokulawula izinsiza zakho zezezimali kuzo zonke izinkundla.

wallet.title: Ukulawulwa Kwesikhwama
wallet.description: Isikhwama esiphephile sezimali eziningi esinokulandelela ibhalansi yesikhathi sangempela, umlando wezintengiselwano, namakhono okulula okufaka/ukukhipha.

transactions.title: Umlando Wezintengiselwano
transactions.description: Amarekhodi enemininingwane yezintengiselwano anezihlungi ezithuthukile, amandla okuthekelisa, nemigwaqo yokuhlola ephelele yazo zonke izenzo zezezimali.

transfers.title: Ukudluliswa
transfers.description: Amasevisi okudlulisa angaphakathi nangaphandle anokucubungula ngokushesha, izimali ezincintisanayo, kanye nokusekela imali yamazwe ngamazwe.

investments.title: Ukutshalwa Kwezimali
investments.description: Amathuba okutshalwa kwezimali ahlukahlukene nezinhlelo zokuhlaziya ezisezilingeni lochwepheshe, amathuluzi okuhlola ubungozi, nokulandelela ukusebenza kuzo zonke izigaba zezimpahla.

plans.title: Izinhlelo Zokutshalwa Kwezimali
plans.description: Amasu okutshalwa kwezimali akhethiwe anezinkomba zobungozi ezinemininingwane, idatha yokusebenza komlando, nemibandela eguquguqukayo ukuhambisana nezinhloso zakho zezezimali.

staking.title: Imiklomelo Ye-Staking
staking.description: Thola imali engajahile ngokusebenzisa i-cryptocurrency staking ngamazinga e-APY ancintisanayo, izikhathi zokukhiya eziguquguqukayo, nokusabalalisa kwemiklomelo okuzenzakalelayo.

ico.title: Ukuthengiswa Kwamatokeni
ico.description: Ukufinyelela kwasekuqaleni kuma-Initial Coin Offerings ahlolwe kahle ngemibiko yokuhlola ephelele, ukuhlaziywa kwe-tokenomics, nokulandelela ukutshalwa kwezimali.

marketplace.title: Imakethe
marketplace.description: Hlola izimakethe ezisezingeni eliphezulu zezinto zedijithali nezenyama ezinezintengiselwano ezivikelekile, abathengisi abaqinisekisiwe, nokuvikelwa kwabathengi okugcwele.

nft.title: Igalari Ye-NFT
nft.description: Thola, dala, futhi ushintshanise izimpahla zedijithali ezihlukile emakethe yethu ye-NFT ekhethiwe enamakhono okufaka isabelo kanye nemali yabadali.

store.title: Isitolo
store.description: Imakethe esezingeni eliphezulu enemikhiqizo yedijithali neyenyama enokucubungula kwenkokhelo okuvikelekile, ukuthunyelwa emhlabeni wonke, nokuvikelwa kwabathengi.

services.title: Amasevisi
services.description: Amasevisi ochwepheshe namathuluzi okuthuthukisa isipiliyoni sakho sokuhwebelana, kufaka phakathi izinhlelo ze-affiliate, izinsiza zemfundo, nokusekelwa okukahle.

affiliate.title: Uhlelo Lwe-Affiliate
affiliate.description: Yenza imali ngenethiwekhi yakho ngohlelo lwethu oluphelele lwe-affiliate olunekhomishana encintisanayo, ukulandelela ngesikhathi sangempela, namathuluzi okumaketha.

support.title: Isikhungo Sokusekela
support.description: Ukusekelwa kwamakhasimende ochwepheshe ngokuphathwa kwamathikithi, amandla wengxoxo ebukhoma, nokuphathwa kwe-akhawunti ezinikele kubasebenzisi abakahle.

faq.title: Isisekelo Solwazi
faq.description: Amadokhumenti aphelele, izifundo, nemibuzo evame ukubuzwa ukusiza ukuthi usebenzise ngokugcwele amandla enkundla.

insights.title: Ukuqonda
insights.description: Ukuhlaziywa kwemakethe kochwepheshe, ukuqonda kokuhwebelana, nezindaba zemboni kusuka eqenjini lethu lezazi zezezimali nabacwaningi bemakethe.
